        <TextBox x:Name="textBox1" HorizontalAlignment="Left" Margin="146,136,0,0" TextWrapping="Wrap" Text="&#xD;&#xA;CHECK SYMPTOMS:&#xD;&#xA;• Distortion where straight lines appear&#xD;&#xA;wavy or bent&#xD;&#xA;• Dark patches or empty spaces appearing&#xD;&#xA;in the centre of your vision&#xD;&#xA;In addition, key symptoms may also include:&#xD;&#xA;• Distinguishing faces becomes a problem&#xD;&#xA;• Difficulty with reading or any other activity&#xD;&#xA;that requires fine vision&#xD;&#xA;• Increased need for illumination, sensitivity&#xD;&#xA;to glare, decreased night vision or poor&#xD;&#xA;colour sensitivity.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;If you experience any of the above symptoms or&#xD;&#xA;any changes in your vision, immediate referral&#xD;&#xA;to an optometrist or ophthalmologist is critical.&#xD;&#xA;Never dismiss any changes in vision as part of&#xD;&#xA;getting older. Early detection can save your sight." VerticalAlignment="Top" Height="474" Width="1055" IsReadOnly="True" FontSize="37.333" TextAlignment="Center" TextChanged="textBox1_TextChanged"/>

    </Grid>
</Page>
